race.comment: VIALE (6) improved again, finishing just 0.8L from the winner over 1000m at this track, racing on the speed. Fitter again and suitably placed. Maps well and can go one better. WANTSOMEMOREOFIT (9) resumes and races well on the fresh side. Has pieces of form in stronger that read well, and she'll go close if presented on song. DARTH INVADER (1) is quick and can clear the awkward gate. Was backed off the map winning his Maiden here by a space and can take the next step without surprise. BLUISH HUE (4) won a trial and looked a run short here first-up. Was tried in Stakes grade prior and is a quick improver. WARILLA GORILLA (2) will be fitter and may be the best of the rest.
